metadata.name: City from the Sky
metadata.description:
A city where the foundation is the clouds and where you have to be careful not to fly too close to the ground.

The inhabitants will see earth cities as unusual, because they don't fear "falling down" or "crashing" they way those people do.

It's an "Epic" because, it takes your mind where it wouldn't go by itself. It makes you think a little, it makes you wonder.
